<para>Hardware spinlocks are dynamically allocated via spin_lock_claim_unused() to avoid conflicts with SDK-internal usage.</para>
<para>Compiled when: PICO_BOARD &amp;&amp; !ARDUINO &amp;&amp; SYN_USE_MULTICORE </para>
